tables.table_schema:
CREATE TABLE Targets (
  target_id INT PRIMARY KEY,
  target_name VARCHAR(50) NOT NULL,
  location VARCHAR(100),
  movement_history VARCHAR(500)
)

CREATE TABLE manipulations (
   manipulation_id INT PRIMARY KEY,
   target_id INT,
   manipulation_type VARCHAR(255),
   manipulator_name VARCHAR(255),
   meeting_location VARCHAR(255),
   CONSTRAINT fk_target
      FOREIGN KEY (target_id)
      REFERENCES targets(target_id)
);

CREATE TABLE Locations (
    location_id INT PRIMARY KEY,
    location_name VARCHAR(50) NOT NULL,
    address VARCHAR(100),
    city VARCHAR(50),
    country VARCHAR(50)
);

CREATE TABLE Movements (
    movement_id INT PRIMARY KEY,
    target_id INT,
    location_id INT,
    movement_date DATE,
    method VARCHAR(50)
);

CREATE TABLE movements (
    movement_id INT PRIMARY KEY,
    target_id INT NOT NULL,
    time TIMESTAMP NOT NULL,
    location VARCHAR(255) NOT NULL,
    FOREIGN KEY (target_id) REFERENCES targets(target_id)
);

CREATE TABLE manipulations (
    manipulation_id INT PRIMARY KEY,
    tactic_id INT NOT NULL,
    movement_id INT NOT NULL,
    success BOOLEAN NOT NULL,
    FOREIGN KEY (tactic_id) REFERENCES tactics(tactic_id),
    FOREIGN KEY (movement_id) REFERENCES movements(movement_id)
);
